# Flappy Bird Gravity

This project is a simple implementation of the classic Flappy Bird game with added gravity mechanics. The objective of the game is to navigate the bird through obstacles without hitting them.

## Features

- Classic Flappy Bird gameplay
- Gravity mechanics that affect the bird's movement
- Simple and intuitive controls
- Score tracking

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone https://github.com/Cambrian34/FlappyBird.git
    ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```
    cd flappybirdgravity
    ```

    ```
#Requirements
- Go 1.16 or higher



## Usage

To start the game, run the following command:

    go run .